  <brief_title>Randomized Control Study of Dermal Staples vs Subcuticular Sutures on Postoperative Scar After Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Control Study of Dermal Staples vs Subcuticular Sutures on Postoperative Scar After Thyroidectomy</official_title>
